o can tap on the card using `tapOn: id: "swipe_card_$userId"`. Good.\n\n   - **P
otential Blocking issue**: The `HomePage._onHorizontalDragEnd` calls `_submitSwi
pe` which does:\n     ```dart\n     Future.delayed(const Duration(milliseconds: 
